Dataset representing the road network in Oldenburg, Germany

Source: R/data.R
net_oldenburg_raw.Rd

See info in the 'data-raw' folder to see how this dataset was created

Usage

net_oldenburg_raw

Format

An object of class sf (inherits from data.frame) with 1738 rows and 9 columns.

Examples

net_oldenburg_raw
